article.description: — Josip Vrankic had 24 points as Santa Clara got past Idaho State 62-49 in the season opener for both teams on Wednesday.
article.headline: Vrankic scores 24 to lead Santa Clara past Idaho St. 62-49
article.linkText: Vrankic scores 24 to lead Santa Clara past Idaho St. 62-49
article.story: SANTA CLARA, Calif. -- — Josip Vrankic had 24 points as Santa Clara got past Idaho State 62-49 in the season opener for both teams on Wednesday. Jalen Williams had 13 points for Santa Clara. Jaden Bediako added nine rebounds. Tarik Cool had 11 points for the Bengals. Malik Porter added 10 points.
